Summary :
---------
Crazy Old Guy is a video game created for the C++ Rush of EPITA in December
2015. This game is a stealth game which has as a purpose to check what we learn
after the workshop week of C++.

To help us in the creation of our project, we used SFML to handle various
information of the game as the window, the time, and so on..


Synopsys :
----------
In "Crazy Old Guy", you embody an old man who just discovered a way to become
invisible. Thus, he tries to escape the CIA that want to capture him, due to
his discovery.


Gameplay :
----------
The whole point of the game is based on this ability and to win,
you must go from one side of the room to the other, while avoiding the enemies
in your way and the different lasers. However, be careful because your
power is limited and at some point, it will be totally over (and not usable
anymore). If this happens, you still have a change to escape your enemies
thanks to wholes in the walls in which you can hide (by pressing E).


Others :
--------
It is also possible to change the costume for aestethic reasons, by pressing
the Q key.


Side note :
-----------
Thank you for playing this game, in which we put all of our heart and that
make us proud !

